article.description: — Aaron Clarke scored 19 points as Sacred Heart beat Lafayette 74-67 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Clarke, Watson lift Sacred Heart past Lafayette 74-67
article.linkText: Clarke, Watson lift Sacred Heart past Lafayette 74-67
article.story: EASTON, Pa. -- — Aaron Clarke scored 19 points as Sacred Heart beat Lafayette 74-67 on Thursday night. Alex Watson added 17 points for the Pioneers, while Tyler Thomas chipped in 15. Bryce Johnson had 12 points for Sacred Heart (3-5). Neal Quinn had 20 points and eight rebounds for the Leopards (2-5). Leo O'Boyle added 15 points. Tyrone Perry had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
